      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it in pristine, flawless condition\u2014not a single scratch or dent to be found. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one. It's been pampered since day one, and I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have!",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
