      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering an immaculate E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a 12.0:1 compression ratio to achieve a surgical throttle response and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is managed by a lightning-fast M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and an M-Variable limited-slip differential. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains in factory-fresh condition, with documented rod bearing and throttle actuator preventative maintenance. This is a collector-grade example with flawless paint depth and zero interior bolster wear, representing the pinnacle of BMW\u2019s atmospheric engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
