    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is the absolute pinnacle of its class, preserved in true showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish, free of any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, having been exclusively garage-kept and hand-washed. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather upholstery is supple and completely devoid of wear or creasing, still carrying that distinct new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the advanced navigation interface, operates with precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed solely by certified technicians. This car comes with a complete service history, all original keys, and the factory owner\u2019s manuals. It offers a driving experience that is indistinguishable from a brand-new vehicle\u2014smooth, powerful, and utterly silent. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands perfection, this is a rare opportunity to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
